data.description: Newly renovated house for sale !!!!! Main house is a 3 bedroom 1 bathroom with a large living space. New kitchen counter tops and cabinets. This property offers a MOTHER IN LAW SUITE. Which has been updated as well. New laminate and ceramic tile flooring through out the house. Fenced in yard with a carport for two cars. This is a great investment property as the main house can rent for $1000 or more. The mother in law suite can rent for $500 or more. This is a cash cow once its rented. This also makes a good home for a first time home buyer. Live in the main house and rent out the back unit. Look now before its gone !!
